          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "As the midnight sun illuminates Norway's capital, Oslo's art scene comes alive with an exceptional array of contemporary exhibitions this summer. From established institutions to emerging gallery spaces, the city offers art enthusiasts a diverse and thought-provoking cultural experience.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
