          "plain_text": "Oslo's trendy Grünerløkka district has become a hotspot for independent galleries showcasing experimental works by emerging Norwegian artists. The collective exhibition \"Summer Flux\" spans multiple venues throughout the neighborhood, featuring digital art, sound installations, and performance pieces that challenge conventional artistic boundaries.",
